OL,3,CCouncil stands by its man for
OL,4,CInternational Women's Day event
OL,6,FIn a statement to UTV, Newry, Mourne
OL,7,Fand Down District Council said: "The
OL,8,Ftheme of our International Women's Day
OL,9,Fevent this year is 'Inspire Inclusion'.
OL,11,F"After careful consideration of
OL,12,Fpotential speakers, Newry, Mourne and
OL,13,FDown District Council was delighted to
OL,14,Fannounce that Billy Dixon, an
OL,15,Finternationally renowned motivational
OL,16,Fspeaker and brand consultant, had
OL,17,Faccepted our invitation to be one of
OL,18,Four speakers at our International
OL,19,FWomen's Day event.
